        "title": "Static Error: This class does not have a static void main method accepting String[]",
        "body": "<p>I'm learning, I'm newbie\nbut I wanted to know what I do to get \"run\" it.\nthis happening a error:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Static Error: This class does not have a static void main method accepting String[].\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This is the code:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>/**\n * @author \"LionH\"\n */\npublic class Caneirinho {\n\n    public static void contar() {\n        int i = 1;\n        String a = \" Carneirinho\",\n            b = \" pulando a cerca.\",\n            c = \"s\";\n\n        for (i = 1; i &lt;= 100; i++) {\n            if (i == 1) {\n                System.out.println(i + a + b);\n            } else {     \n                System.out.println(i + a + c + b);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n} // Carneirinho\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
